# Output file name
Output demo.gif

# Terminal Settings
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# --- START THE DEMO ---

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

# Save a URL
Type "vm save https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/p/visual-attention-variants"
Sleep 300ms
Enter

# Wait for AI processing + success panel
Sleep 15s

# Hold the success panel
Sleep 2s
